title: Ask HN: Android now forcing App updates?
text:

I'm seeing all apps updated yesterday, and auto/manual selector nowhere to be found. Android One v11.

Ash HN: How do you distribute or shard Stable Diffusion?
text: A lot of HN has been having fun with stable diffusion.  Do we really need 1 x GPU with 10GB of RAM?  How do you distribute or "shard" a model you're training?  Could we get this running on the raspberry pi clusters we all have?  Hook it up to OpenFaaS too.
